<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠١١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/549">إِسْحَاقُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6844">وَهْبٌ </a>قَالَ: أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5461">مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ أَبِي بَكْرٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3098">عَبَّادِ بْنِ تَمِيمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3665">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ زَيْدٍ </a>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> اسْتَسْقَى فَقَلَبَ رِدَاءَهُ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>